sanarik is a 2014 horror manipur film directed by l. rajesh and produced by khelen mangang , under the banner of mosbran films . the film features baby rekha heigrujam in the titular role with lairenjam olen , nirmala , edhou , mangoljao , merina , thoibi and dhanamanjuri in the lead roles . it is a feature film about an abnormal girl who is being harassed because of her looks and colour . the film was released at manipur film development corporation ( mfdc ) , palace compound on 28 january 2014 .